# üåê What is Computer Network? (Simple Hinglish Notes)<br>

## 1. Definition & Purpose (Asli Matlab Kya Hai?)<br>
**Definition:**<br>
Jab do ya do se zyada computers aur devices (jaise printer, mobile) ek saath jude hote hain taaki wo aapas mein baat kar sakein aur cheezein share kar sakein, toh usse hum **Computer Network** kehte hain.<br>

**Analogy (The Tea Stall):**<br>
Socho ek chai ki dukaan hai. Agar wahan waiter, cook, aur cashier aapas mein baat nahi karenge, toh tum tak chai kabhi nahi pahunchegi. Networking bilkul wahi 'link' hai jo sabko jorta hai taaki kaam (data transfer) ho sake.<br>

**Purpose (Maqsad):**<br>
- **Data Sharing:** Ek file ko dusre computer tak bhejna.<br>
- **Resource Sharing:** Ek hi printer ko poore office ke 10 computers se chalana.<br>
- **Communication:** Email, chat, aur video calls karna.<br>

## 2. Why Networks Exist (Zarurat Kyun Padi?)<br>
Pehle ke zamane mein agar tumhe ek file dusre computer mein chahiye hoti thi, toh tumhe 'Floppy Disk' ya CD mein copy karke bhagte huye jana padta tha (Isse purani bhasha mein Sneakernet kehte the).<br>

Networks isliye banaye gaye taaki:<br>
- **Speed:** Palkein jhapakte hi data hazaron kilometre door pahunch jaye.<br>
- **Cost-Effective:** Har computer ke liye alag printer ya scanner kharidne ki zarurat nahi.<br>
- **Storage:** Tum apna data 'Cloud' (Google Drive) par save kar sako jo kahin se bhi access ho jaye.<br>

## 3. Evolution: ARPANET to Internet (Networking ka Itihaas)<br>
Ye kahani badi filmy hai!<br>

**The Beginning (ARPANET):**<br>
1960s mein US Department of Defense ne ek project banaya jiska naam tha **ARPANET**. Unhone pehli baar do computers ke beech message bheja... Maze ki baat ye hai ki wo sirf "LOGIN" likhna chahte the, lekin system crash ho gaya aur sirf "LO" pahuncha!<br>

**Growth:**<br>
Dhire-dhire aur bhi universities aur scientist isse judne lage.<br>

**The Internet:**<br>
Jab alag-alag networks aapas mein judne lage (Network of Networks), tab janam hua **Internet** ka.<br>

**Analogy:**<br>
ARPANET ek chhoti si gali thi, aur Internet aaj ka poora "Highway System" hai jo poori duniya ko connect karta hai.<br>

## 4. Network Applications (Networking Kahan Kaam Aati Hai?)<br>
Aaj tum jo bhi online karte ho, wo networking ki wajah se hai:<br>
- **Email (SMTP):** Digital chittiyan bhejna.<br>
- **Web Browsing (HTTP/HTTPS):** Websites dekhna jaise Google ya Facebook.<br>
- **File Transfer (FTP):** Badi files upload ya download karna.<br>
- **Real-time Gaming:** PUBG ya Free Fire khelte waqt server tumhare moves ko miliseconds mein process karta hai.<br>
- **E-commerce:** Amazon/Flipkart se shopping karna.<br>
